<view class="pageDemo"><mx-nav title="搜索组件" /><view style="padding-top:{{navHeight}}rpx;"></view><title>搜索组件（示例）</title><desc>组件名称：Search</desc><desc>搜索场景的输入框组件，在信息池中缩小范围，快速而轻松地获取目标信息。</desc><line /><title type="h2">组件分解示例图片</title><desc>Todo待补充</desc><line /><wrap><title type="h2">搜索栏样式</title><desc>属性：styleType，normal / insert</desc><mx-search styleType="normal" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="insert" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">值</title><desc>属性：value</desc><mx-search styleType="normal" value="纳兰忱" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="insert" value="纳兰忱" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">是否显示搜索图标</title><desc>属性：showSearchIcon，是否显示搜索图标</desc><desc>属性：searchIconColor，搜索图标颜色</desc><desc>属性：searchIconSize，搜索图标大小，默认48</desc><mx-search showSearchIcon="{{true}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search showSearchIcon="{{true}}" searchIconColor="#f00" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search showSearchIcon="{{true}}" searchIconSize="40" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search showSearchIcon="{{false}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">占位文本</title><desc>属性：placeholder，默认"请输入"</desc><desc>属性：placeholderColor，占位文本颜色</desc><mx-search placeholder="请输入关键词" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search placeholder="请输入关键词" placeholderColor="#f00" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">光标颜色</title><desc>属性：cursorColor</desc><mx-search cursorColor="#1677FF" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">是否显示清除按钮</title><desc>属性：showClear</desc><mx-search value="纳兰忱" showClear="{{true}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search value="纳兰忱" showClear="{{false}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">是否显示按钮</title><desc>属性：showBtn，是否显示按钮</desc><desc>属性：btnText，按钮文案，默认"搜索"</desc><desc>属性：btnColor，按钮文本色</desc><mx-search styleType="normal" showBtn="{{true}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="normal" showBtn="{{true}}" btnText="取消" btnColor="#1677FF" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="insert" showBtn="{{true}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="insert" showBtn="{{true}}" btnText="取消" btnColor="#1677FF" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">搜索栏背景色</title><desc>属性：bgColor</desc><mx-search styleType="normal" showBtn="{{true}}" bgColor="#c0daff" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="insert" showBtn="{{true}}" bgColor="#c0daff" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">预设关键词</title><desc>属性：keyword，关键词文本</desc><desc>属性：keywordBgColor，预设关键词背景色</desc><desc>属性：keywordColor，预设关键词文本色</desc><mx-search styleType="normal" showBtn="{{true}}" keyword="手机" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="normal" showBtn="{{true}}" keyword="手机" keywordBgColor="#c0daff" keywordColor="#f00" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><view class="bg"><mx-search styleType="insert" showBtn="{{true}}" keyword="手机" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></view><line /><view class="bg"><mx-search styleType="insert" showBtn="{{true}}" keyword="手机" keywordBgColor="#c0daff" keywordColor="#f00" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></view></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">是否显示返回按钮</title><desc>属性：showBack，是否显示返回按钮</desc><desc>属性：backColor，返回图标颜色</desc><mx-search styleType="normal" showBack="{{true}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" /><line /><mx-search styleType="normal" showBack="{{true}}" backColor="#f00" bind:search_change="handleChange" /></wrap><line /><wrap><title type="h2">事件</title><desc>事件：bind:search_change，值变更事件</desc><desc>事件：bind:search_back，返回按钮点击事件</desc><mx-search styleType="normal" showBtn="{{true}}" showBack="{{true}}" bind:search_change="handleChange" bind:search_back="handleBack" /></wrap><line /></view>